description:
LED strip lights are a great option for those that want to modernize their home. LED lights can mimic the light of the moon, which is perfect for those that want a relaxing atmosphere. With all the different colors and shapes available, it's easy to find the perfect fit for any room style. These lights are also portable which makes them easier to install at any location within your house.

One of the best features of LED lights is that they are much more durable than older, traditional light bulbs. With a long lifespan and no need for replacement costs, your new LED strip lights will save you a lot of money over time.

We know you love to light up the night. And we got just what your home needs—this Tech Vision Electronics product. This 5-meter strip of 16 different colors has anti-static bags that ensure there are no issues with static cling and 60 LEDs per meter for a fantastic display. It’s 10 mm wide and 2.5 mm thick so no installation is too tough!
name: LED Strip Lights
